article.description: — Dillon Jones scored 21 points to help Weber State defeat Sacramento State 58-53 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Jones scores 21 to help Weber State earn 58-53 victory over Sac State
article.linkText: Jones scores 21 to help Weber State earn 58-53 victory over Sac State
article.story: OGDEN, Utah -- — Dillon Jones scored 21 points to help Weber State defeat Sacramento State 58-53 on Saturday night. Jones also added five assists and three steals for the Wildcats (16-9, 7-5 Big Sky Conference). Steven Verplancken Jr. had 12 points and Alex Tew scored eight. Duncan Powell finished with 17 points for the Hornets (6-19, 2-10), who have lost eight in a row. Austin Patterson totaled 12 points and three steals. Jacob Holt scored 11 with seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
